sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular
    participant GW as Gateway YARP
    participant BE as Writer BE
    participant RC as rag_client
    participant RAG as rag-service
    participant OAI as OpenAI

    FE->>GW: POST /apps/writer/api/chat with Bearer JWT and conversation_id
    GW->>BE: forwards Bearer
    BE->>BE: optional_user decodes JWT and extracts user_id
    BE->>RC: retrieve user_id conv_id last_user_msg
    RC->>RC: mint internal JWT with 60s TTL
    RC->>RAG: POST /api/retrieve with Bearer
    RAG->>RAG: embed query and run top-k cosine search
    RAG-->>RC: chunks list
    RC-->>BE: chunks
    BE->>BE: format context and build citations
    BE->>OAI: stream with system prompt plus context
    loop tokens
        OAI-->>BE: chunk
        BE-->>FE: data line with token
    end
    BE-->>FE: sources event with citations array
    BE-->>FE: data DONE marker
